473
00:47:06,030 --> 00:47:07,030
Co?

474
00:47:11,030 --> 00:47:12,430
Zapomeň na to, pokud nevíš.

475
00:47:17,900 --> 00:47:19,030
Vím všechno.

476
00:47:21,670 --> 00:47:22,830
Tak pak je to dobře.

477
00:47:31,400 --> 00:47:32,430
Já...

478
00:47:33,570 --> 00:47:35,170
